### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### =============================================
### Health & Info
### =============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health HTTP/1.1

###

### API Info (Index)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ HTTP/1.1

###

### Vector Store Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/stats HTTP/1.1

###

### List Models (OpenAI-compatible)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/models HTTP/1.1

### =============================================
### Chat Endpoints
### =============================================

### Simple Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What is retrieval augmented generation?",
    "include_reasoning": false
}

###

### Chat with Reasoning
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "How does embedding similarity search work?",
    "include_reasoning": true
}

### =============================================
### RAG Endpoints
### =============================================

### RAG Query (with reasoning)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/query HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "What are the key components of an agentic RAG system?",
    "include_reasoning": true
}

###

### RAG Query (without reasoning)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/query HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "Explain the reflection module in AI agents.",
    "include_reasoning": false
}

###

### Retrieve Context Only
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/retrieve HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "vector database embeddings",
    "top_k": 5
}

###

### Retrieve Context (custom top_k)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/retrieve HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "prompt engineering techniques",
    "top_k": 3
}

### =============================================
### Evaluation
### =============================================

### Evaluate with Test Questions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/evaluate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "test_questions": [
        { "question": "What is RAG?" },
        { "question": "How do vector databases work?" },
        { "question": "What is the role of embeddings in search?" }
    ]
}

### =============================================
### OpenAI-Compatible Endpoints (used by Open WebUI)
### =============================================

### Chat Completions (OpenAI format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer dummy-key

{
    "model": "rag-agent",
    "messages": [
        { "role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant." },
        { "role": "user", "content": "What is retrieval augmented generation?" }
    ],
    "temperature": 0.7,
    "max_tokens": 500
}

###

### Chat Completions - Multi-turn Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer dummy-key

{
    "model": "rag-agent",
    "messages": [
        { "role": "user", "content": "What are embeddings?" },
        { "role": "assistant", "content": "Embeddings are numerical vector representations of text." },
        { "role": "user", "content": "How are they used in RAG systems?" }
    ],
    "temperature": 0.7
}
